## Eval Results

| Scenario | Score | Route |
|---|---|---|
| Critical chest volume gap | 0.75 | coaching вҶ’ gpt-4o |
| Stalled bench during cut | 0.75 | coaching вҶ’ gpt-4o |
| Overreaching / deload | 1.00 | coaching вҶ’ gpt-4o |
| Shoulder injury modification | 1.00 | coaching вҶ’ gpt-4o |
| Research: volume during deficit | 1.00 | research вҶ’ gpt-4o-mini |
| Arm volume gap identification | 0.75 | coaching вҶ’ gpt-4o |
| Simple data lookup | 1.00 | lookup вҶ’ none |

